<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-122-200  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 122 200.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  Feb 6 1990 v4 n5 p3(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Coastal Associates Publishing L.P. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>VideoQuill livens up text. (Data Translation Inc introducesVideoQuill character-generation program) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Guglielmo, Connie.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Data Translation Inc. (product introduction).andO;Ticker:    DATX.andO;Product:   VideoQuill (Computer font) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     FontsProduct IntroductionText FormattingImage GenerationGraphics Software.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By Connie GuglielmoandM;Marlboro, Mass.andP;  -- Data Translation Inc. last week introduced VideoQuill, acharacter-generation program that lets users have fun with fonts.andM;The $495 program, due in early March, contains nine outline fonts that can beresized, stretched, distorted and rotated in one-degree increments.andP;  Fontsare automatically anti-aliased to produce smooth edges when displayed on boththe Mac screen and lower-resolution video monitors.andM;Data Translation will offer a library containing 47 additional outline fontsfor $495.andP;  In addition, the program will work with Apple's forthcoming Royalfonts, according to Data Translation.andM;VideoQuill lets users work with 24-bit color PICT or TIFF images as eitherbackgrounds or fills for the text.andP;  Grad-uated color backgrounds and colorfills for text also can be created with the program.andM;Other features include:andM;andgt;Kerning and leading controls.andM;andgt;Drop shadows.andM;andgt;Type transparency densities that can be varied from 5 percent to 100percent.andM;andgt;Basic drawing and layout tools.andM;Type can be superimposed over or filled with video images using any videoboard.andP;  Data Translation's own 16-bit ColorCapture board is directlysupported by the program.andM;To save disk space, VideoQuill contains a reference function that displays aversion of the VideoQuill-generated file in other documents without creatingadditional copies of the VideoQuill file on disk.andP;  Changes made to anyrelated VideoQuill documents will be reflected in other documentsautomatically, the company said.andM;VideoQuill requires a Mac II series machine running Apple's 32-bit colorQuickDraw, a color display and at least 2 Mbytes of RAM.andM;Data Translation Inc. is located at 100 Locke Drive, Marlboro, Mass.andP;  01752;(508) 481-3700.andP;  n</TEXT></DOC>